nl.tno.sensorstorm.api.annotation

Annotation Type OperationDeclaration


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=TYPE)
public @interface OperationDeclaration
    Annotation for the Operation. There can be three parameters (inputs, outputs and metaParticleHandlers). The inputs is mandatory and the other two are optional.

    • Required Element Summary

      Required Elements 
      Modifier and Type Required Element and Description
      Class<? extends DataParticle>[] inputs
      An array containing one or more types of DataParticles that this Operation can process.

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      Class<? extends MetaParticleHandler>[] metaParticleHandlers
      An array containing zero or more MetaParticleHandlers that must be instantiated and connected to this operation.
      Class<? extends DataParticle>[] outputs
      An array containing zero or more types of DataParticles specifying the dataParticles this Operation produces.

    • Element Detail

      • inputs

        public abstract Class<? extends DataParticle>[] inputs
        An array containing one or more types of DataParticles that this Operation can process.

      • outputs

        Default:
        {}

      • metaParticleHandlers

        public abstract Class<? extends MetaParticleHandler>[] metaParticleHandlers
